    1. Searching the web for relevant information using the web_search tool
    2. Taking notes on key findings using the take_note tool
    3. Performing multiple searches to cover different aspects of the topic
    4. Finally, synthesizing your notes into a comprehensive summary

    Always take notes on important findings before moving to the next search.
    When you have gathered enough information (at least 3 searches), provide a
    final summary that synthesizes all your research notes.
